Paper: hep-th/0210036

Date: 2002-10-03

Title: Ghost condensates in Yang-Mills theories in nonlinear gauges

Authors: A.R. Fazio, V.E.R. Lemes, M.Picariello, M.S. Sarandy, S.P. Sorella

Comments: 9 pages, final version to appear in Mod. Phys. Lett. A

Ghost condensates of dimension two are analysed in a class of nonlineargauges in pure Yang-Mills theories. These condensates are related to thebreaking of the SL(2,R) symmetry, present in these gauges.